      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREUKELEN (4) well-bred Farnan gelding from the good mare Tavarnelle on debut for the Mel O'Gorman yard. Impressed in both trials and gets his chance from the good draw. Expected to go close. MOKE LAKE (2) looks the best of the raced brigade with his hoof on the till. Gave his all with the 59kg with a tough third over 1000m at Scone. Hard to beat in this suitable race. JUSTO'S ROCKET (5) big improver second-up when he attacked the line to finish second over 1000m at Dubbo. Has further improvement to come and can measure up against some of these. BRAVALATANTE (9) resumes with the claim after going out a narrow third over 1300m at Moree last December. Look for her late.",
